      <title>圭亚那因误报设备价值将埃克森美孚告上法庭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/guyana-takes-exxon-to-court-over-misstated-value-of-equipment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[圭亚那税务机构正在将埃克森美孚公司告上法庭，此前该公司的一名供应商表示，该公司错误地将油井设备的价值夸大了 200 倍，达到约 120 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/guyana-takes-exxon-to-court-over-misstated-value-of-equipment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 21:38:01 GMT</pubDate>
